mber 2018, Renan joined [[Campeonato Brasileiro S\u00e9rie B]] side [[Esporte Clube S\u00e3o Bento|S\u00e3o Bento]] on a one-year contract.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ecsaobento.com.br/site/news.php?page=1&id=1028&t=S%C3%A3o_Bento_anuncia_contrata%C3%A7%C3%A3o_de_goleiro_Renan_e_lateral_Guilherme_Rom%C3%A3o|title=S\u00e3o Bento anuncia contrata\u00e7\u00e3o de goleiro Renan e lateral Guilherme Rom\u00e3o|publisher=[[Esporte Clube S\u00e3o Bento]]|date=13 December 2018|accessdate=14 December 2018|language=Portuguese}}</ref>\n\n==International career==\nRenan was a member of [[Brazil Olympic football team|Brazil]]'s team for the [[Football at the 2008 Summer Olympics|2008 Summer Olympics]], he was the first-choice goalkeeper for the tournament, appearing in all matches as Brazil went on to get the bronze medal.\n\n==Honours==\n\n===Club===\n;Internacional\n* [[Campeonato Ga\u00facho|Rio Grande do Sul State League]]: 2005, 2008, 2011, 2012\n* [[Copa Libertadores]]: [[2006 Copa Libertadores|2006]], [[2010 Copa Libertadores|2010]]\n* [[FIFA Club World Cup]]: [[2006 FIFA Club World Cup|2006]]\n* [[Recopa Sudamericana]]: [[2007 Recopa Sudamericana|2007]], [[2011 Recopa Sudamericana|2011]]\n\n;Goi\u00e1s\n* [[Campeonato Goiano|Goi\u00e1s State League]]: 2013\n\n===International===\n;Brazil\n* [[2008 Beijing Summer Olympics|2008 Summer Olympics]]: Bronze medal winner\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n* {{BDFutbol|8476|Renan}}\n* {{Sambafoot|1005_Renan_Brito.html|Renan}}\n* {{in lang|pt}} [https://web.archive.org/web/20071125110524/http://www.renan1.com.br/renan/ renan1.com.br]\n* {{Soccerway|renan-brito-soares/9401/}}\n\n{{Brazil men's football squad 2008 Summer Olympics}}\n\n{{Use mdy dates|date=May 2015}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Renan Brito Soares}}\n[[Category:1985 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Brazilian footballers]]\n[[Category:Brazil youth international footballers]]\n[[Category:Brazil under-20 international footballers]]\n[[Categ